.TH LYRICD 1
.SH NAME
lyricd - serve lyrics
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lyricd
[
.B -d
] [
.BI -a " addr"
]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B Lyricd
serves lyrics over a simple protocol.  It searches for and retrieves
lyrics from various websites on the internet, cleans up the lyrics and
returns them.  The protocol has not yet been documented.
.PP
Option
.B -d
enables debugging output.
The address to listen on can be changed with
.B -a
.IR addr ,
the default is
.IR net!localhost!7115 .
.PP
These sites are currently searched in:
azlyrics, elyrics, lyrc, sing365, rarelyrics, lyricsdownload, plyrics, darklyrics.
.SH SEE ALSO
.IR lyric (1),
.IR lyrics (2)
